{"tid":168505,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死2隻]山泥傾瀉掩埋5人　2名長者送院後不治","createTime":"2017-03-23T14:51:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T14:51:55.000Z","uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba293abd409292202d33373d44a3649bdc160dbd","tid":168505,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:51:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170323/bkncn-20170323185009967-0323_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170323%2Fbkncn-20170323185009967-0323_05011_001.html&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eMKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=581712ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170323/bkncn-20170323185009967-0323_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170323/photo/bkncn-20170323185009967-0323_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170323%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170323185009967-0323_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=a29ac241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖北十堰房縣今日凌晨發生山泥傾瀉事故，造成5人被活埋，其中3人成功自行逃生，另外2名六旬老人經送院搶救後證實不治。當地政府部門目前已對事發現場附近道路、山坡進行整治。<br />\n<br />\n有目撃者指，現場是一間數年前因工程建設而搭建的臨時房屋，當地市民以低價購入居住。事發時，屋內5人被困，其中3人所住的房間在塌方位置的邊緣位置，故能自行脫困，另外2名六旬老人卻不幸被困。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}